      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl316_LabelType\">The spirit voices of your ancestors sing to you of the world around you.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl316_LabelType\">Bekyar Human Heritage or Shoanti Human Heritage</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl316_LabelType\">Once per day, you can act in the surprise round even if you aren&rsquo;t aware of your attackers; you can use this action only to start a bardic song or raging song, and you&rsquo;re still considered flat-footed until you act in the first normal round of combat.</span></p>",
